data.description: Discover the charm of Dix Hills in this spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath Colonial on a tranquil tree-lined street. Perfectly situated in a friendly neighborhood within the coveted Half Hollow Hills school district, this home exudes warmth and potential. Enjoy the idyllic scene of kids biking and families strolling with their dogs. The residence offers a fantastic layout, hardwood floors, and a full basement brimming with possibilities. Recent updates include a brand-new roof, gutters, eaves, lighting, as well as newer windows and central AC. With endless possibilities for personal aesthetics, this is your chance to make your mark in Dix Hills - seize it!
